null,"duedate":null,"progress":{"progress":0,"total":0},"customfield_11806":null,"comment":{"comments":[{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/21176/comment/45258","id":"45258","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=juphoff","name":"juphoff","key":"juphoff","accountId":"557058:c2c52741-c1d7-497e-87c9-57845be682d0","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Jeff Uphoff","active":false,"timeZone":"America/New_York"},"body":"Now I remember why I left the clientkey.pem file world-readable: it has to be readable by the eucalyptus user (or whatever user is defined as EUCA_USER in eucalyptus.conf), which is what the client side of the migration is running as. If it's not readable by EUCA_USER, migrations won't work.\n\nA couple of options:\n\n1. Leave it as is, readable by nonprivileged users (which it has to be anyway).\n2. Change the keys to be owned by the EUCA_USER defined in eucalyptus.conf, which probably doesn't provide us with significant additional security in the event of an instance breach.\n\nI'm implementing #2 above. ","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=juphoff","name":"juphoff","key":"juphoff","accountId":"557058:c2c52741-c1d7-497e-87c9-57845be682d0","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Jeff Uphoff","active":false,"timeZone":"America/New_York"},"created":"2013-05-10T11:11:18.664-0500","updated":"2013-05-10T11:11:18.664-0500"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/21176/comment/45283","id":"45283","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=rusvika","name":"rusvika","key":"rusvika","accountId":"557058:0f138bdf-f1d0-4468-9edd-e45575af47da","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Vika Felmetsger","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"I think #2 is OK for the purpose of restricting access to the key. However, I just had a discussion with [~gholms] about whether it makes sense to store migration keys and certs (especially since some of them are owned by the eucalyptus user) in a host-wide directories (/etc/pki/) which are potentially used by other application on the same host. This especially applies to CA creds when we put NC's credentials into /etc/pki/CA directory and making it a trusted authority for the whole host, not just libvirt. Since libvirt config allow to specify custom directories for key stores, it would be better to put all these key/certs into some eucalyptus owned directories ([~gholms] can consult on more on the best practices here)\nI don't think this part is 3.3 critical, but if we don't change it now, we should consider it for later (and open another ticket?).","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=rusvika","name":"rusvika","key":"rusvika","accountId":"557058:0f138bdf-f1d0-4468-9edd-e45575af47da","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/c975ce5391bf03e1a9aa2a957435569b?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Drusvika%26avatarId%3D10701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Vika Felmetsger","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2013-05-10T14:08:57.234-0500","updated":"2013-05-10T14:08:57.234-0500"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/21176/comment/45287","id":"45287","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=juphoff","name":"juphoff","key":"juphoff","accountId":"557058:c2c52741-c1d7-497e-87c9-57845be682d0","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Jeff Uphoff","active":false,"timeZone":"America/New_York"},"body":"From my reading of the libvirt code, while libvirtd (the daemon) allows config-file specification of the server-side key/cert, the client-side path is compiled into the library as /etc/pki/libvirt/clientcert.pem, though it appears a $HOME/.pki/libvirt path may also be supported. I can play with this post-3.3.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=juphoff","name":"juphoff","key":"juphoff","accountId":"557058:c2c52741-c1d7-497e-87c9-57845be682d0","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/11a22041bb5fb0250638e57dc0ddf8c5?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Djuphoff%26avatarId%3D10503%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Jeff Uphoff","active":false,"timeZone":"America/New_York"},"created":"2013-05-10T14:39:09.983-0500","updated":"2013-05-10T14:39:09.983-0500"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/21176/comment/46153","id":"46153","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=shaon","name":"shaon","key":"shaon","accountId":"557058:1e5e1aa5-5986-4a9e-b9ed-814f7000cd4f","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/70d1c1681d03ea38518d3b4f59db4385?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dshaon%26avatarId%3D11900%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/70d1c1681d03ea38518d3b4f59db4385?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dshaon%26avatarId%3D11900%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/70d1c1681d03ea38518d3b4f59db4385?s=16&d=htt